runs.comm: tossed up and dropped short and wide outside off, gets away with it as the cut finds the fielder

poor calling! Amjad pushed it towards point, set off, then quickly turned back because there was no single, the fielder unfortunately let the ball slip out of his hand in the urgency so the ball dropped in the middle of nowhere
he flicks it away to the leg side
tossed up and he comes forward to defend
he fires this one wide down the leg side
much slower through the air and he gently dabs it  to third man
trapped high on the pads, and he played all around it
moves it away and he hangs his bat out and dabs it down to third man
he tries to flick it to the leg side and is trapped on the pad, skidded through

appeal for a caught behind! Amjad swings at it and misses it outside off, the keeper Wilson did really well to catch it diving to his right and there was an appeal, Erasmus reckoned it only clipped the pad, good decision
works it away to the on side
tries to force it wide of the bowler but Sorensen stops it
that's more like it! As straight as it gets, this was pitched up on off stump and he gave that quite a thud down the ground
suspect calling again, gently tucked to the on side, set off and turned back
flatter one and he knocks it to midwicket and they do well to hurry for the second run
tossed up slow and wide outside off, he tries to whack it out of the ground but misses, just about drags his foot back
loses control of this one and fires it wide down the leg side
tossed up and he gets forward to defend
plays all around it and the ball strikes the pads and rolls away

would have been an amazing catch, tossed up outside off, Asif aims straight but gets an outside edge that goes to third man, short third man runs after it but the ball evades him, Poynter does well to dive and save a boundary
bangs it in short and he pulls to deep square leg
pitched up on the pads and flicked away to the leg side
inside edge to the pads and they sneak in a single
short fine leg is in place, Sorensen errs by bowling straight, easy swing for Amjad, finds the big gap at deep square leg
suspect calling again! This was smashed to mid-off, Asif was ambling out of his crease and had to get back quickly, throw was wide
smashed that! This was banged short and wide outside off and he whacks it over backward point
that was cheeky! Well played. Slip was very wide and Asif knew that, he hung his bat out and deliberately steered it past the gap between the keeper and slip
quick bouncer, swing and a miss and even the keeper couldn't hold on to it properly
he chops it to the off side
he aims for the on side and plays too early, the ball hits the pad and rolls away
shorter ball and he tucks it to the on side

appeal for a run-out and Asif looks in trouble! And he's a couple of yards short. He tucked it to the on side and set off for a run that never existed, Murtagh sprinted forward, picked up and under-armed it to the keeper Wilson, Asif had turned around and was struggling to get back
pitched outside leg and struck his pads, the ball rolls to the off side
gets beside the line and chops it towards point
on the pads and forcefully flicked away to deep square leg
well played, this was a bit too straight, a bit short, read the length well and pulled to deep square leg, picked the gap
lovely shot by Khurram, this was a half volley wide outside off, there was a gap at cover to be exploited and he went forward and smashed it
that was easy! Stirling tossed that up outside off and dropped it short, tempted Amjad to go for the airy cut, catching practice to short third man, the bowling change works
continues round the wicket, he gets forward and defends

that's two for the over! Another soft dismissal, Stirling tosses it up from round the wicket, Patil went down the pitch and looked to flick it over midwicket, no elevation at all and an easy catch for Porterfield at short midwicket
hits his pads and rolls away to the on side
he goes back and works it to the on side
this was a slower ball outside off and dabbed towards third man
a bit too straight and he flicks it wide of midwicket
there's a direct hit at the striker's end, dabbed towards third man and he sets off, Anwar grounds his bat and he's safe
tucks him up for room and he defends
keeps it straight again  and Anwar can only push it back to the bowler
fullish outside off and he pushes it wide of mid-off
tossed up outside off and he drives it in the air over point
pushes it on the pads and he works it wide of square leg
he goes back and works it to the on side
tossed up and no room, he can only defend
drops it short and he looks to smash that but straight to cover
went a long way! Tossed up outside off, Anwar made room to free his arms and sent that sailing over wide long-off
keeps it outside off and he dabs it down to third man
a bit too straight and he clips it straight to midwicket
he drifts a bit too wide down the leg side
well bowled, slightly slower and straight, could only push it back to the bowler
slower ball outside off and he angles it down to third man
another slower one and he gently dabs it down to third man
the off cutter and he flicks it forcefully wide of midwicket, good work in the deep by Thompson
follows the movement and angles it down to third man
that went several miles! That was short and it wasn't the quickest ball, Anwar pulls and his bat speed sends that sailing several rows over deep square leg
slams it in the air to deep cover
Khan tries to pinch the gap at backward point but Porterfield does well to slide to his left and save it
a bit straight and he pushes it to the on side
slower ball and he works it straight to mid-on
slower ball and he works it to mid-on
Khan looks to paddle that from outside off, hits his body and rolls away
looks to biff that wide of midwicket, can't beat the fielder
slower ball and he drives this one down the ground to long-off
Khurram had a chance to cut this away but couldn't beat point
no room to work with, looked to pinch the gap at point
wide outside off and he mistimes the cut towards point
drops that short and he mistimes the pull to the deep
cramps him for room and he chops it to point, Khurram needs to try something different
he tries to innovate by giving room but can only force it to long-on
slower ball and pushed towards deep midwicket and they run the first one quickly
tucked towards deep midwicket  but they will be limited to a single only
slower ball and he forces it down to long-on
he bowled this full and wide outside off, Khurram makes too much room and has to really reach for that, outside edge to third man
makes room and carves it over point, didn't time it well
gets away with a full toss as Anwar can only find long-off
yet another full toss and it's only a single, flicked to deep square leg
biffed straight back to the bowler and good reflexes by O'Brien, this was a length ball and Anwar looked to pull, instead flat-batted it back to the bowler
fullish ball on the pads and he works it to deep midwicket
drifts on middle and leg and he works it down to fine leg
another soft dismissal! Khurram's struggle ends, he was looking to whack this over the on side, not in control and the top edge swirls to cover, easy take
good length on middle and off and worked to midwicket
this was short and he was too early on the pull, the ball hits his body and rolls away
it's a slower ball and he makes room and carves that to deep cover, didn't pick the gap
well bowled, he made room and he saw that and fired that wide of the leg stump, could only drive back to the bowler
low full toss and he drills it down to long-on
cramps him for room and he pushes it towards point
fullish in length on the off stump and pushed to cover
moves across the stumps and another slower one, checks his shot to the off side
steers it just wide of backward point and they manage to pick up a second
this was dragged too short and wide outside off and he makes room and bashes that to long-off, UAE need plenty more
inswinging yorker and he makes room and fails to dig it out
he made room and he fired that full and wide outside off, he hopes for a wide call
good bowling again, Javed backs away too much and he gets his bat down hoping to get some wood on it
makes room and heaves a fuller ball down to deep midwicket
he walks right across his stumps and can only guide a low full toss to third man, the 100's up. Too late?
makes room to a fuller ball and gets an outside edge that drops towards third man
he makes room and looks to smash that and ends up swishing at air
another swing and a miss, the short ball this time
he finally finds the boundary, this one was full and he came a few paces forward and hit through the line to the straight boundary
made room to a short delivery and pulled him down to deep midwicket
this was banged in short
a low full toss wide outside the off stump and he mistimes it to the off side
makes room to a low full toss and can only push it to the long-off
makes room to a fuller delivery and he can't get it past cover
good yorker, just wide of the off stump and he made room and failed to get bat on it
rightfully put away, this was a friendly full toss outside off and he smashes it over extra cover, beats the fielder in the deep
switches to a length ball and he makes room and looks to pull in front of square, slaps it straight to long-on
slower ball and he makes room and tries to slog it away, mistimed but beats midwicket
runs across his stumps and looks to play the ramp shot over short fine leg but misses it completely, hits the keeper
Dropped by Thompson at long-off, really should have taken that, Mustafa skied that and Thompson ran to his right and floored it
full outside off and driven wide of point
tries to ramp this over short fine leg again but this time it deflects off the keeper
full on the leg stump and looks to tickle it past short fine leg again, can't pinch that gap and it's only a single
